      • registerDataBroadcastReceiver

        public void registerDataBroadcastReceiver(com.smartpos.dualscreen.DataBroadcastReceiver receiver,
                                          com.smartpos.dualscreen.DataBroadcastFilter filter,
                                          String broadcastPermission,
                                          android.os.Handler scheduler)
                                   throws DeviceException
        Register a DataBroadcastReceiver to the context.

        DataBroadcast is a broadcast provide by the system, which can transfer between main and sub screens.Only the DataBroadcastReceiver can receive the DataBroadcast.

        Parameters:
        receiver -
        filter -
        broadcastPermission - The permissions that a broadcaster must hold in order to send to this receiver. If null, no permission is required.
        scheduler - Handler identifying the thread that will receive the Intent. If null, the main thread of the process will be used.
        Throws:
        DeviceException

      • setAutoExitSub

        public void setAutoExitSub(boolean autoExit)
                    throws DeviceException
        If you close an apk's all main screen activities, that apk's sub screen activities will automatically close too.

        The auto exit sub feature of each apks is closed by default, which means the sub screen activity will keep running when main screen activities closed. 当主屏的 activity 都关闭了以后，客屏的 activity 是否自动关闭。

        Parameters:
        autoExit -
        Throws:
        DeviceException
